{"tid":1130160,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙里：我值得繼續教車路士","createTime":"2019-04-29T00:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T08:21:33.000Z","uid":19552,"like":16,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"df06ba306095fdc715cf8ace75812fe1d140da70","tid":1130160,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T00:17:40.000Z","msg":"車路士領隊沙里認為憑首個賽季的表現，值得爭取來季繼續帶隊；他謂若得到更多時間、有整個夏天讓他訓練球隊的話，車路士成績必然更佳。<br />\n<br />\n沙里話車仔今季好成功之中<br />\n車路士現時正力爭英超前四位置，而且亦打入歐霸盃4強有力爭標，沙里自覺有能力讓車路士變得更好。他說：「我上個夏天很遲才來到，未能做足整個季前準備。在拿玻里我有60課防守操練，但今季初只有11、2課，這並不足夠。若我繼續當領隊，車路士會有所進步。」<br />\n<br />\n車路士將面對2個轉會窗不能買人，沙里表示：「我認為力保現時球隊主力，比引進新血來得更重要，我會為此努力。」(<a href=\"http://goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoal.com&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9WAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=0fabc3e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"e7d4df714b163c91a20e4faa391799d38b9b87bf","tid":1130160,"uid":163937,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T00:43:10.000Z","msg":"提早返歸食煙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c534b93728304d7bceb199bdc70cb30b99961a","tid":1130160,"uid":70195,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T00:47:39.000Z","msg":"返意甲養老先岩沙蛇"},{"pid":"87e009890e75dff328eefb7e1ce8492423310439","tid":1130160,"uid":90726,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T00:57:22.000Z","msg":"我地干地接手就拎英超<br />\n你條死煙鏟咁撚多嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔知邊度黎既自信"},{"pid":"47ffbd2f40ffd6766fa5e723c1f850c46ee6cd3a","tid":1130160,"uid":33601,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T01:10:03.000Z","msg":"死廢佬呃飯食"},{"pid":"97178577e7eb9ed6579d56de96df28d274957eb4","tid":1130160,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T01:41:39.000Z","msg":"煙sir返去教阿朗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f97bc747084fc247ae52588f